Shadowcaster turned to face the young Maximal, a
gentle smile on his face.

"It's been a while little cat. No, you're not seeing a
ghost- I have Primus to thank for that. He brought me
back to be his champion.  No longer am I meant to
watch over merely the Maximals and Autobots, my role
is now to watch over ALL his children. However, there
is not much time for a reunion- Unicron draws closer
and time draws shorter. We must recover the Matrix
from Tripredacus hands."

 --- OMWOS <o_mighty_wife_of_shinigami@...>
wrote: 
---------------------------------
Cheetor's eyes bounced back and forth between everybot
that spoke, 
trying to figure out who was who and what was what and
what the color 
purple tasted like. He gave a shake of his head when
he heard his name 
and turned around, spotting a oh so familar bot and
blinked in 
surprise. He rubbed a paw over his eyes to make sure
there wasn't any 
oil in them and took a second look. 

By the Matrix, his circuits must have been fried in
the battle, he was 
seeing ghostsparks. "Shadowcaster?"

OMWOS
